CONTROLLER EKA SAHA MODEL EKA -
    mulinma karanne web page eka hadaganna eka passe

    after creating buttons have to create the 
                            controller in the cmd so write in 
                            command line:
                            php artisan make:controller CreatesController
                            
                            app->Http=>controllers=> maked controller

                            then we have to create a model
                            php artisan make:model modelname -m

                            database->migrations->..

                            php artisan migrate
                            if there is an error please follow
                            stack overflow it has it 
                            by changing the code plese drop down
                            all tables in the data base and 
                            run php artisan migrate in the cmd
                            then it will make four tables

        controller ekai model ekakui hada gannawa

        ita passe database eke migrations eke table ekak hadagannawa
        ita passe hadapu controller eken function ekak hadala model ekata cal karana eka thama
        karanne

        ita passe route eken call karala balanawa wadada kiyala

        controller eken pass karanawa table eke data eka variable ekakin eka home eke di allagannawaa
        @walin home eke tinne eka thama eken table ekata ganata data danawa

        ita passe create eka hadanawa 

CREATE PAGE EKE WADA TIKA-
    meke wenna one submit button eka click karama insert kiyala wenama page ekata
    yannath one database ekata data save wennath one.so at first
    action eka {{url('/insert')}} danawa inset ekata yannanam route karanna one
    enisa route eke post method eken conroller eke add kiyala funtion ekak hadanawa
    controller eketh add kiyana eka hadanna one mokada route eke controller eken
    add kiyana ekata call karana nisa.return 'add' kiyala one nam inset ekata yanawada
    kiyala balanna puluwan.

CREATE PAGE EKA VALIDATE KEREEMA=
    mekedi add function eke request object ekak hadala karana widiha controller 
    eke thinawa.e tika create page eke wada karanna one code tikath validation 
    yatathe liyala thinawa.mekedi controller eke tinawa array eke title and description 
    kiyala dekak e name deka aniea title lable eke input eke name ekama wenna one
    description ekatath ehemai.ehema nati unoth errors dekama pennanawa.column
    dekama fill karath success wenne naha.
